fields.name: o_Status_Desc
fields.expression:
decode(true, 
reg_match(status_desc, 'Pending Cancellation.*'),'Cancel Notice',
reg_match(status_desc, 'Non.*renewed.*') and Policy_Expiration_Date >=SYSDATE,'Nonrenewed (inforce)',
reg_match(status_desc, 'Non.*renewed.*') and Policy_Expiration_Date < SYSDATE,'Nonrenewed (expired)',
status_desc)
